  "itemdesc-atlatl": "A Spearman Grandmaster polearm with a reinforced Starsteel head. Requires the Spearman Grandmaster skill to craft.",
  "item-towershield": "Tower Shield",
  "itemdesc-towershield": "Strong frontal protection with substantial handling costs. Requires the Shield Grandmaster skill to craft.",
  "item-armorpaddingkit": "Armor Upgrade Kit",
  "itemdesc-armorpaddingkit": "Permanently raises an armor piece or shield's maximum durability by 20%. Each item can be upgraded once. Requires the Tank Grandmaster skill to craft.",

